- **FR-002**: System MUST validate email format and password minimum 8 characters
- **FR-003**: System MUST allow users to authenticate with JWT
- **FR-004**: System MUST allow CRUD operations on roles
- **FR-005**: System MUST allow CRUD operations on usuarios
- **FR-006**: System MUST track last login timestamp
- **FR-007**: System MUST allow soft delete of users

#### Infraestructura (co.edu.unbosque.mundial2026.infraestructura)
- **FR-008**: System MUST allow CRUD operations on sedes
- **FR-009**: System MUST allow CRUD operations on estadios
- **FR-010**: System MUST validate Estadio belongs to Sede
- **FR-011**: System MUST allow listing estadios by sede

